---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 447
  - Title: Kama-Sutra
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Subversion-The Wrathful Side=Corruption
---
The ancient and venerable authors are of opinion that Auparishtaka is
the work of a dog and is not worthy of a man. It is a low practice and
opposed to the orders of the Scriptures.
